{"tid":2064274,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"耶撚真係好撚煩","createTime":"2020-06-14T16:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T02:54:25.000Z","uid":73959,"like":10,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d417f6929a7516560b358cb161aaf75d5490db","tid":2064274,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"班耶撚根本就係被人洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人可以證明到耶穌真係存在過？<br />\n上年香港人俾人打到仆街<br />\n偉大嘅耶穌又去撚咗邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班耶撚成日都滿口仁義道德<br />\n口就講信主唔做得呢樣 唔做得嗰樣<br />\n其實轉個頭咪又係衰嘢做盡<br />\n未婚搞大肚大把啦<br />\n講完粗口講大話之後去禱告就得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係職場上咪又係爾虞我詐 有幾可拎個心出嚟對人？<br />\n基本上我識朋友第一件事 就係問佢有冇信教<br />\n天主教同基督教嘅我一律唔撚會同佢做朋友<br />\n成班教會喺度圍威喂 根本同邪教冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"39848b8361435e763f6741b1f56659252129c273","tid":2064274,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"快啲嚟感化我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58a897f3842dbe283d143a71c724b951e965f28","tid":2064274,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"old news is so 唔識串"},{"pid":"26acd3d20074097c3cc0f58cecf30fc44722f22f","tid":2064274,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"唔好買六合彩喎 信主唔可以賭博㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070fa096288fef66550b275cccd169178c521020","tid":2064274,"uid":341279,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:23:54.000Z","msg":"有宗教都得罪你？"},{"pid":"7f6d8c6fc0a5914665c560e9298fe46e13093ef8","tid":2064274,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"基本上大台教會都係藍嫁啦<br />\n要辦學  唔得罪得政府"},{"pid":"4258c9df9ee1313bcd5